00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:22,461
"Ne moeš pobjeci od Ijubavi. "

3
00:01:23,253 --> 00:01:26,840
To je bio oglas
u Baltimorskim novinama.

4
00:01:27,924 --> 00:01:30,760
I tako ju je on našao.

5
00:01:32,094 --> 00:01:35,764
Ona je bila mlada ena
u potrazi za muem.

6
00:01:36,223 --> 00:01:39,059
On je bio muškarac u potrazi
za suprugom.

7
00:01:59,119 --> 00:02:01,037
Prekasno za govoriti mu razumno.

8
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:03,414
Ne moeš ju oeniti.
Nisi ju nikad sreo.

9
00:02:03,498 --> 00:02:07,501
Srest cu je danas. Brod iz Amerike
dolazi u 6:00, oenit cemo se u 9:00...

10
00:02:07,627 --> 00:02:09,170
...u 10:00, vratit cu se na posao.

11
00:02:09,587 --> 00:02:12,089
Smiješno. To je smiješno.

12
00:02:12,131 --> 00:02:16,676
Covjek treba enu, nije li to ono
sto si mi govorio? Poslao sam po jednu.

13
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:17,719
Iz Amerike.

14
00:02:17,802 --> 00:02:19,387
Kako ona izgleda?

15
00:02:20,972 --> 00:02:24,183
Doğe dan u ivotu svakog muškarca
kada band svira...

16
00:02:24,267 --> 00:02:28,687
...a on je jedini koji to cuje.
Danas je tvoj dan.

17
00:02:29,188 --> 00:02:30,856
Volim te.

18
00:02:31,607 --> 00:02:33,066
Ona nije prekrasna.

19
00:02:33,358 --> 00:02:35,527
Nije ni trebala biti prekrasna...

20
00:02:35,610 --> 00:02:38,821
...samo dobra, iskrena i dovoljno
mlada da rodi djecu.

21
00:02:39,947 --> 00:02:44,785
Hajde. Sunce ce uskoro izaci.
Brod ce doci.

22
00:02:46,787 --> 00:02:50,957
Ali što je s Ijubavlju, Luis?
Zar ne bi tu negdje trebalo biti i Ijubavi?

23
00:02:51,374 --> 00:02:53,543
Ljubav nije za mene, Alan.

24
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:55,920
Ljubav je za one Ijude
koji vjeruju u nju.

25
00:02:57,422 --> 00:02:58,506
Idemo.

26
00:02:59,799 --> 00:03:03,093
Zašto mi se smiješ?
Smiješ mi se cijelo jutro.

27
00:03:03,135 --> 00:03:05,679
Nema veze. Idi! Hajde!

28
00:04:23,208 --> 00:04:26,044
Ne, ovo nije Ijubavna prica.

29
00:04:26,711 --> 00:04:31,382
Ali je prica o Ijubavi, i snazi
koju ima nad našim ivotom.

30
00:04:32,299 --> 00:04:35,177
Snazi da ozdravi ili uništi.

31
00:04:44,394 --> 00:04:46,896
I ovdje prica pocinje.

32
00:05:03,369 --> 00:05:04,412
Mr. Vargas?

33
00:05:06,706 --> 00:05:08,165
Luis Vargas?

34
00:05:09,875 --> 00:05:11,835
Ne prepoznajete me, zar ne?

35
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:17,298
Miss Russell?

36
00:05:18,550 --> 00:05:19,717
Da.

37
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:24,555
Julia Russell?

38
00:05:26,724 --> 00:05:28,392
Ali, ova slika-

39
00:05:28,434 --> 00:05:32,521
Prevarila sam vas.
Zao mi je. Nisam trebala.

40
00:05:33,396 --> 00:05:35,940
Bila sam nesigurna. Vidite...

41
00:05:36,566 --> 00:05:40,361
...nisam eljela da se zainteresirate
za mene samo zbog moje Ijepote.

42
00:05:41,904 --> 00:05:45,741
Zato sam poslala sliku neke
druge ene, a ne vlastitu.

43
00:05:48,410 --> 00:05:50,245
Vidim.

44
00:05:50,495 --> 00:05:54,165
Nadam se da cete mi oprostiti.
Mislila sam pisati puno puta. Probala sam.

45
00:05:54,415 --> 00:05:56,876
Ali hrabrost me je napustila. Pa sam...

46
00:06:03,674 --> 00:06:05,008
I...

47
00:06:09,346 --> 00:06:12,849
Sad stojim pred vama kakva jesam,
i mislite sve najgore.

48
00:06:13,182 --> 00:06:14,350
Ne, ne.

49
00:06:15,518 --> 00:06:17,019
Nije baš tako loše.

50
00:06:18,687 --> 00:06:21,857
Samo, nije ono što sam oèekivao.

51
00:06:22,858 --> 00:06:26,027
Ako je moja prevara
promijenila vaše namjere...

52
00:06:26,194 --> 00:06:27,862
...ako niste zadovoljni-

53
00:06:27,946 --> 00:06:29,197
Ne, nije to.

54
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:32,533
...spremna sam se vratiti kuci
u Delaware.

55
00:06:32,658 --> 00:06:34,952
- Ako elite, vratit cu se.
- Miss Russell...

56
00:06:36,704 --> 00:06:38,038
Miss Russell...

57
00:06:41,708 --> 00:06:43,543
...bili ste iskreni sa mnom.

58
00:06:44,211 --> 00:06:46,546
I ja cu biti s vama.

59
00:06:48,506 --> 00:06:50,967
I ja cu priznati svoju prevaru.

60
00:06:54,845 --> 00:06:56,930
Ali vi izgledate isto kao
na slici.

61
00:06:57,056 --> 00:06:58,640
Da izgledam.

62
00:06:59,516 --> 00:07:02,143
Ali pisao sam vam da sam slubenik...

63
00:07:02,227 --> 00:07:05,230
...u firmi za izvoz kave. Ali nisam.

64
00:07:08,441 --> 00:07:09,859
Ja posjedujem firmu.

65
00:07:10,693 --> 00:07:12,319
To je moj biznis.

66
00:07:17,658 --> 00:07:20,243
Niste htjeli da se zainterisram
za vas...

67
00:07:20,327 --> 00:07:23,079
...samo zbog vašeg velikog
bankovnog racuna.

68
00:07:24,580 --> 00:07:25,623
da.

69
00:07:29,293 --> 00:07:31,462
Onda imamo nešto zajednickog.

70
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:35,048
Ne moe nam se vjerovati.

71
00:07:39,678 --> 00:07:44,307
Naravno, ako je moja prevara
promijenila vaše namjere...

72
00:07:46,934 --> 00:07:50,604
...ako niste zainteresirani za
udaju za bogatog covjeka...

73
00:07:51,563 --> 00:07:53,815
Ne, mislim da je to u redu.

74
00:07:56,318 --> 00:07:59,237
Ako vama ne paše
nešto zgodnija ena.

75
00:08:01,906 --> 00:08:03,699
Potrudit cu se.

76
00:08:19,047 --> 00:08:20,381
Miss Russell.

77
00:08:22,258 --> 00:08:23,592
Mr. Vargas.

78
00:08:25,094 --> 00:08:28,347
Sada imamo svo vrijeme
na svijetu da se upoznamo.

79
00:08:29,181 --> 00:08:31,099
Ne, ne svo vrijeme.

80
00:08:33,435 --> 00:08:35,853
Vjencat cemo se u 9:00.

81
00:08:37,772 --> 00:08:40,066
Onda bolje da pourimo.

82
00:08:51,951 --> 00:08:53,411
"Uzmi ovaj prsten...

83
00:08:54,287 --> 00:08:56,122
"... kao znak moje Ijubavi...

84
00:08:58,249 --> 00:08:59,667
"... i vjernosti...

85
00:09:00,084 --> 00:09:01,418
"... prema tebi. "

86
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:28,651
Muzika!

87
00:09:37,826 --> 00:09:40,287
Dame i gospodo, zdravica!

88
00:09:41,288 --> 00:09:44,457
Našem mladoenji i njegovoj...

89
00:09:44,666 --> 00:09:47,126
...ocaravajucoj mladoj!

90
00:09:52,214 --> 00:09:53,882
eliš li plesati sa mnom?

91
00:09:54,174 --> 00:09:55,509
Ples?

92
00:09:57,511 --> 00:09:59,012
Ja ne plešem.

93
00:09:59,596 --> 00:10:01,348
Ja kaem da plešeš.

94
00:10:06,102 --> 00:10:10,523
Neka njihov ivot bude kao ples,
harmonican, lagan.

95
00:10:10,689 --> 00:10:13,525
Ples za citav zivot-

96
00:10:13,650 --> 00:10:15,485
Alan, previše je previše.

97
00:10:15,569 --> 00:10:16,862
Uskoro sam gotov.

98
00:10:16,945 --> 00:10:19,781
Sad si gotov. Sjedi.

99
00:11:10,118 --> 00:11:11,786
- Sve najbolje.
- Hvala.

100
00:11:44,191 --> 00:11:45,901
Da li eliš pogledati kucu?

101
00:11:45,984 --> 00:11:48,820
Ne. Mogu je pogledati sutra.

102
00:11:52,782 --> 00:11:55,743
Daj mi par trenutaka.
Malo me je sram.

103
00:11:56,952 --> 00:12:01,540
Dat cu ti onoliko trenutaka,
dana, noci koliko trebaš.

104
00:12:03,959 --> 00:12:05,794
Kada eliš da doğem k tebi...

105
00:12:06,628 --> 00:12:07,962
...doci cu.

106
00:12:09,172 --> 00:12:10,506
Ne prije.

107
00:12:15,928 --> 00:12:17,388
Ucinit ces to za mene?

108
00:12:19,431 --> 00:12:21,099
Ako eliš, budem.

109
00:12:28,189 --> 00:12:29,524
Onda...

110
00:12:30,274 --> 00:12:32,109
...laku noc.

111
00:12:37,322 --> 00:12:39,324
Soba je tamo, desno.

112
00:12:40,283 --> 00:12:42,243
Mislim da cu je naci.

113
00:13:55,351 --> 00:13:57,186
Konacno si budan.

114
00:13:59,230 --> 00:14:00,856
Dan je vec napola prošao.

115
00:14:03,692 --> 00:14:05,527
Oprosti. Nisam obucen.

116
00:14:05,611 --> 00:14:08,405
Mogu sacekati vani,
ali kava ce se ohladiti.

117
00:14:08,739 --> 00:14:10,198
Ne, u redu je.

118
00:14:10,699 --> 00:14:14,160
Ako mi neko bude nosio kavu
svako jutro prije nego što se obucem...

119
00:14:14,285 --> 00:14:16,329
...bit cu jako sretna.

120
00:14:16,913 --> 00:14:18,372
To ce promijeniti dan.

121
00:14:18,497 --> 00:14:19,582
Ali...

122
00:14:20,291 --> 00:14:22,251
...Ti piješ samo caj.

123
00:14:22,334 --> 00:14:24,002
Da? Ne.

124
00:14:24,753 --> 00:14:28,590
Kad sam pisao da radi u firmi za
proizvodnju kave ti si napisala-

125
00:14:28,673 --> 00:14:30,341
To je bila moja sestra.

126
00:14:31,134 --> 00:14:35,680
Vjerovala je da je kava grešno zadovoljstvo
pa sam se pretvarala da se slaem.

127
00:14:35,763 --> 00:14:39,975
Citala je sva moja pisma tebi,
pa nisam uvijek mogla biti iskrena.

128
00:14:43,729 --> 00:14:47,690
Još jedan razlog da ih zaboraviš.
To je sve sad iza tebe.

129
00:14:49,859 --> 00:14:51,569
Sto misliš?

130
00:14:53,237 --> 00:14:54,697
O cemu?

131
00:14:57,783 --> 00:15:00,077
Da li misliš kao i moja sestra...

132
00:15:00,786 --> 00:15:04,122
...da je uivanje uvijek grešno?

133
00:16:02,550 --> 00:16:05,052
Zašto si izabrao enu iz Amerike?

134
00:16:07,179 --> 00:16:09,431
Mi smo ovdje prošlost.

135
00:16:11,016 --> 00:16:12,809
Vi ste tamo buducnost.

136
00:16:15,270 --> 00:16:18,356
Zašto si odabrala odlazak?

137
00:16:19,357 --> 00:16:21,526
Da pobjegnem od buducnosti.

138
00:16:23,402 --> 00:16:25,905
Da postanem netko drugi.

139
00:16:29,074 --> 00:16:31,910
Netko sam drugi s tobom.

140
00:16:34,287 --> 00:16:35,955
Netko više kao...

141
00:16:36,789 --> 00:16:38,124
...ja.

142
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:58,559
Tamo, u njegovom zagrljaju...

143
00:16:59,018 --> 00:17:00,978
...postala je netko drugi.

144
00:17:02,771 --> 00:17:04,773
Netko, netko kao ona sama.

145
00:18:47,825 --> 00:18:50,452
Kaem ti, nikad nisam bio sretniji.

146
00:18:51,161 --> 00:18:53,622
Ne postoji "sretno oenjen".

147
00:18:53,705 --> 00:18:56,541
To je nelogicno, kao "sretno mrtav".

148
00:18:58,126 --> 00:19:01,712
Mislio sam da ces se do sada
vec vratiti kurvama.

149
00:19:01,796 --> 00:19:03,631
Ici malo svojim kreolkama.

150
00:19:03,673 --> 00:19:04,799
Ne više.

151
00:19:04,924 --> 00:19:07,259
Imao si ju za sebe
vec dovoljno dugo.

152
00:19:07,343 --> 00:19:09,178
Kad cemo ju ponovno vidjeti?

153
00:19:09,261 --> 00:19:11,179
Idemo u kazalište slijedeci tjedan.

154
00:19:11,263 --> 00:19:13,431
Americki zabavljaci koje
eli vidjeti.

155
00:19:13,515 --> 00:19:14,766
Pridrui nam se.

156
00:19:22,648 --> 00:19:26,610
Soon comes the morning
when the knell is rung...

157
00:19:26,985 --> 00:19:29,154
...to take my living breath.

158
00:19:29,237 --> 00:19:31,489
Come, come, the night is almost done.

159
00:19:36,202 --> 00:19:37,828
Satan is near!

160
00:19:38,663 --> 00:19:40,581
The shrieking, grim and...

161
00:19:40,664 --> 00:19:43,917
...hideous brim of hell to uncover.

162
00:19:44,168 --> 00:19:47,003
Come, or you will share her wretched end.

163
00:19:47,337 --> 00:19:50,006
Hellhound! Abominable monster!

164
00:19:50,340 --> 00:19:52,508
Would that I had never been born!

165
00:19:57,346 --> 00:19:59,014
Prekrasno.

166
00:19:59,348 --> 00:20:00,683
Odvratno.

167
00:20:01,350 --> 00:20:02,809
Jeftina melodrama.

168
00:20:04,436 --> 00:20:09,107
Was it we who forced our way to you?
Who was it sent her to her ruin?

169
00:20:09,440 --> 00:20:10,775
I...

170
00:20:12,026 --> 00:20:13,361
...or you?

171
00:20:14,195 --> 00:20:17,656
What evil thing has risen from the ground?

172
00:20:18,198 --> 00:20:22,160
Father, let angels now have charge of me...

173
00:20:22,411 --> 00:20:25,246
...encamped around heavenly company.

174
00:20:25,622 --> 00:20:27,415
She is condemned to die.

175
00:20:28,875 --> 00:20:31,460
She is redeemed on high!

176
00:20:31,711 --> 00:20:33,546
Hither, to me!

177
00:20:44,722 --> 00:20:47,892
Julia, draga, izgledas rumeno.

178
00:20:48,476 --> 00:20:51,479
- Jesi dobro?
- Da, to je od kazališta.

179
00:20:51,771 --> 00:20:53,105
Oboavam ga...

180
00:20:53,397 --> 00:20:55,065
...cak i jeftine melodrame.

181
00:20:57,901 --> 00:20:59,069
Oprostite.

182
00:21:05,575 --> 00:21:07,660
Da li pati od groznica?

183
00:21:08,285 --> 00:21:10,913
Pati od malo previše rua.

184
00:21:11,163 --> 00:21:14,666
Glupost. Dama ne stavlja ru.

185
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:16,668
Ne, dama ne.

186
00:21:17,002 --> 00:21:20,672
I dama ne luta sama po
kazalištu.

187
00:21:22,674 --> 00:21:24,008
Oprostite.

188
00:21:28,637 --> 00:21:31,765
Moda ce vam drugi cin
biti bolji.

189
00:22:25,689 --> 00:22:28,733
Oprostite, gospodine!
Publici nije dozvoljeno iza pozornice.

190
00:22:28,817 --> 00:22:30,777
Ne dirajte me.

191
00:22:30,860 --> 00:22:32,779
Dovraga, to je moja ena!

192
00:22:32,862 --> 00:22:34,989
Luis, došao si me spasiti...

193
00:22:35,948 --> 00:22:37,283
...kao u predstavi...

194
00:22:39,285 --> 00:22:41,120
Što radiš ovdje?

195
00:22:41,286 --> 00:22:45,248
Nije li uzbudljivo?
Pogledaj ove cudne naprave.

196
00:22:45,457 --> 00:22:49,169
- Tko je bio taj covjek?
- Koji covjek? Izgubila sam se, to je sve.

197
00:22:49,711 --> 00:22:51,379
Stalo mi je srce zbog tebe.

198
00:22:51,546 --> 00:22:54,507
Osjeti. Osjecaš kako udara?

199
00:22:59,470 --> 00:23:00,471
Isuse.

200
00:23:01,263 --> 00:23:03,014
Umrijet cu zbog tebe.

201
00:23:06,643 --> 00:23:08,311
Nadam se.

202
00:23:12,023 --> 00:23:13,482
Na mjesta, molim.

203
00:23:13,649 --> 00:23:16,151
Dame i gospodo, drugi cin.

204
00:23:24,409 --> 00:23:26,035
Odvedi me kuci.

205
00:23:36,712 --> 00:23:38,880
Draga sestro.

206
00:23:39,005 --> 00:23:44,219
Ne znam zašto si takva sa mnom.
Prošlo je puno tjedana kako si otišla.

207
00:23:44,802 --> 00:23:48,931
Za sve to vrijeme ni rijeci, da me
obavijestiš o svom sigurnom dolasku...

208
00:23:49,181 --> 00:23:53,185
...da li si srela Mr. Vargasa,
da li je bilo svadbe.

209
00:23:53,519 --> 00:23:55,228
Što da mislim?

210
00:23:55,771 --> 00:23:58,523
Kontaktirala sam ambasadu u Havani...

211
00:23:58,732 --> 00:24:01,067
...i vlasti tamo u Santiagu.

212
00:24:01,151 --> 00:24:03,945
Znam što osjecaš prema njoj, ali...

213
00:24:04,612 --> 00:24:05,988
...moraš joj pisati.

214
00:24:08,449 --> 00:24:11,118
Moraš, prije nego
nam pošalje policiju.

215
00:24:11,535 --> 00:24:13,870
U pravu si.
Nisam bila dobra prema njoj.

216
00:24:14,329 --> 00:24:17,499
lako ona nikad nije bila
dobra prema meni.

217
00:24:19,417 --> 00:24:21,419
Samo napravi to.

218
00:24:22,962 --> 00:24:25,256
Napravi to, i onda je gotovo.

219
00:24:25,297 --> 00:24:27,299
Ne, ne, ne!

220
00:24:29,635 --> 00:24:32,971
U redu je. Ja sam, Luis.

221
00:24:34,180 --> 00:24:35,515
Sanjala si.

222
00:24:37,475 --> 00:24:38,768
Jesi u redu?

223
00:24:43,147 --> 00:24:45,482
To je to.

224
00:24:45,816 --> 00:24:48,485
Samo si sanjala.

225
00:24:51,321 --> 00:24:52,656
U redu je.

226
00:24:54,491 --> 00:24:56,284
To je bio samo san.

227
00:24:56,659 --> 00:24:59,912
Ruan san, to je sve.

228
00:25:08,295 --> 00:25:09,462
Bio je samo san.

229
00:25:09,838 --> 00:25:12,048
Jesi OK? Trebaš li nešto?

230
00:25:12,132 --> 00:25:13,091
Tebe.

231
00:25:13,925 --> 00:25:15,259
Zao mi je.

232
00:25:15,593 --> 00:25:17,762
Sad si sa mnom. Sigurna.

233
00:25:18,012 --> 00:25:19,805
Sve je u redu.

234
00:25:20,264 --> 00:25:21,765
Hoces li ostati?

235
00:25:21,974 --> 00:25:23,308
Naravno.

236
00:25:24,518 --> 00:25:25,811
Naravno.

237
00:25:27,646 --> 00:25:29,314
Sve je u redu.

238
00:26:00,759 --> 00:26:02,928
Luis, nemoj ici.

239
00:26:05,263 --> 00:26:07,932
Kako je ovo jutro
kraljica kuce?

240
00:26:12,686 --> 00:26:15,356
Pogledaj. Vidiš? Napisala sam.

241
00:26:17,232 --> 00:26:19,860
Tako je najbolje. Hvala ti.

242
00:26:20,110 --> 00:26:23,905
- Reci cu Sari da pošalje.
- Nema potrebe. Mogu i sam.

243
00:26:23,988 --> 00:26:25,990
Nisam adresirala.

244
00:26:26,074 --> 00:26:30,035
Imam adresu u uredu.
Onda je na putu.

245
00:26:38,752 --> 00:26:40,545
Što ces danas raditi?

246
00:26:40,628 --> 00:26:43,965
Idem Engleskom krojacu
na Plaza Vieja.

247
00:26:47,051 --> 00:26:48,219
Trebat ces novaca.

248
00:26:49,970 --> 00:26:52,681
Potpisite ovdje, Senora.

249
00:26:54,307 --> 00:26:57,602
Da li je to i za osobni i za
poslovni racun?

250
00:26:57,686 --> 00:26:59,229
Da, hvala.

251
00:26:59,604 --> 00:27:02,607
elim da mi ena ima pravo
korištenja svih racuna.

252
00:27:03,024 --> 00:27:04,066
Evo ga.

253
00:27:04,150 --> 00:27:06,402
Da li da potpišem s
djevojackim imenom?

254
00:27:06,861 --> 00:27:08,320
Ne, s vjencanim.

255
00:27:08,612 --> 00:27:12,032
Morate zapamtiti da ponovite
potpis uvijek isto...

256
00:27:12,366 --> 00:27:14,201
...svaki put kad podiete cek.

257
00:27:14,618 --> 00:27:16,244
Pokušat cu.

258
00:27:27,129 --> 00:27:28,755
O, covjece!

259
00:27:37,764 --> 00:27:40,099
Pa, Luis, da li je to
konacno Ijubav...

260
00:27:40,349 --> 00:27:42,309
...ili samo strast?

261
00:27:43,394 --> 00:27:44,770
Ima li razlike?

262
00:27:45,104 --> 00:27:46,271
Ima, ima.

263
00:27:46,480 --> 00:27:50,108
Voljeti nekoga je davanje,
i onda eljeti dati još više.

264
00:27:50,775 --> 00:27:52,277
A strast?

265
00:27:52,777 --> 00:27:54,070
Što je strast, Alane?

266
00:27:54,862 --> 00:27:58,032
Strast je uzimanje, i onda
uzimati još više.

267
00:27:58,324 --> 00:28:01,118
Progutati, konzumirati.
Bez logike, bez razuma.

268
00:28:01,493 --> 00:28:04,329
Pa... uzimanje, davanje.

269
00:28:05,163 --> 00:28:06,498
Koje je?

270
00:28:06,998 --> 00:28:08,291
Oboje.

271
00:28:11,294 --> 00:28:13,254
elim joj dati sve.

272
00:28:14,881 --> 00:28:17,133
I onda joj elim sve uzeti.

273
00:28:18,384 --> 00:28:21,637
O, Luis. Ti si izgubljen.

274
00:28:22,221 --> 00:28:23,555
Ne, ne.

275
00:28:25,599 --> 00:28:27,809
Ona je ta koja je izgubljena.

276
00:28:28,434 --> 00:28:32,104
Kako, zašto, ne znam.
Ali to ce se promijeniti.

277
00:28:33,356 --> 00:28:35,149
Ja mogu to promijeniti.

278
00:28:42,072 --> 00:28:43,156
Mr. Vargas?

279
00:28:45,617 --> 00:28:47,869
Walter Downs.
Nisam vas mislio preplašiti.

280
00:28:48,202 --> 00:28:50,788
- U redu je.
- Receno mi je da vas mogu tu naci.

281
00:28:50,871 --> 00:28:52,373
- Kako vam mogu pomoci?
- Ništa vano.

282
00:28:52,456 --> 00:28:55,376
Skoro nevano.
Zarucio sam se za Miss Russell.

283
00:28:55,459 --> 00:28:56,585
Mislite Juliju?

284
00:28:56,919 --> 00:28:59,254
Ne, Emily. Njezinu sestru.

285
00:28:59,546 --> 00:29:00,672
U Delawareu.

286
00:29:00,714 --> 00:29:02,590
Ja sam privatni istraitelj.

287
00:29:03,007 --> 00:29:04,884
Tek sam stigao iz Wilmingtona.

288
00:29:05,385 --> 00:29:10,014
Razumijem.
Znam da je Miss Russell zabrinuta.

289
00:29:10,056 --> 00:29:13,058
Ali pisali smo joj prije
nekoliko tjedana.

290
00:29:13,434 --> 00:29:17,938
Siguran sam da ce osjetiti veliko
olakšanje kad dobije to pismo.

291
00:29:18,021 --> 00:29:20,023
Znaci Miss Julia je dobro?

292
00:29:20,398 --> 00:29:23,526
Više nego dobro.
I više nije Miss Julia.

293
00:29:23,943 --> 00:29:25,653
Ona je Senora Vargas, moja ena.

294
00:29:25,736 --> 00:29:27,196
Znaci vi ste oenjeni?

295
00:29:29,949 --> 00:29:32,076
- To su odlicne vijesti.
- Sretno oenjeni.

296
00:29:32,159 --> 00:29:33,702
To vidim.

297
00:29:33,827 --> 00:29:36,997
Kakva misterija je sretan brak.

298
00:29:37,580 --> 00:29:40,041
Rumenilo na obrazu,
Sjaj u oku.

299
00:29:40,917 --> 00:29:43,252
- Mislim da se to vidi.
- Vidi se, svakako.

300
00:29:43,336 --> 00:29:45,546
Miss Russell ce biti
sretna da to cuje.

301
00:29:46,130 --> 00:29:48,090
Bilo bi mi drago kad bi
joj to rekli.

302
00:29:48,173 --> 00:29:49,466
Svakako cu joj to reci.

303
00:29:51,176 --> 00:29:54,846
I bit cu još više uvjeren
kad sretnem vašu enu.

304
00:29:58,308 --> 00:29:59,475
Da, da.

305
00:30:00,351 --> 00:30:01,269
Zašto da ne?

306
00:30:04,438 --> 00:30:06,523
Bit cemo doma u nedjelju popodne.

307
00:30:07,274 --> 00:30:09,109
elite li doci na kavu?

308
00:30:09,484 --> 00:30:10,485
Da, doci cu.

309
00:30:10,569 --> 00:30:13,947
Porucite vašoj eni kako se
veselim što cu ju upoznati.

310
00:30:25,707 --> 00:30:27,876
Vani molim. Na terasi.

311
00:30:29,127 --> 00:30:30,462
Napravite kako kae.

312
00:30:33,965 --> 00:30:35,758
Baš na vrijeme.

313
00:30:36,592 --> 00:30:39,762
Ovo je za nedjelju,
a ovo za preko tjedna.

314
00:30:40,346 --> 00:30:42,348
Dobro, dobro.

315
00:30:43,515 --> 00:30:45,100
A ostalo?

316
00:30:45,309 --> 00:30:47,185
Ovo mi se sviğa.

317
00:30:47,978 --> 00:30:50,855
Što misliš?
Ima sedam dana u tjednu.

318
00:30:51,981 --> 00:30:53,983
Zar nema ništa u tvom sanduku?

319
00:30:54,067 --> 00:30:57,820
Ništa dobro.
A, i izgubila sam kljuc.

320
00:30:57,903 --> 00:31:01,490
Pozvat cemo bravara.
Ma to je lako. Zapravo...

321
00:31:01,740 --> 00:31:03,617
...sam cu to napraviti.

322
00:31:05,035 --> 00:31:07,871
Ne, elim ti nešto pokazati. Doği.

323
00:31:09,164 --> 00:31:11,833
Morate sada otici.
Poljubit cu svog mua.

324
00:31:11,958 --> 00:31:14,418
Onda cemo se okupati.

325
00:31:31,517 --> 00:31:33,144
Što to osjecam?

326
00:31:33,853 --> 00:31:35,271
Moj parfem.

327
00:31:35,562 --> 00:31:36,730
Ne.

328
00:31:38,649 --> 00:31:39,983
Cigaru.

329
00:31:41,610 --> 00:31:43,111
Probala sam jednu.

330
00:31:45,405 --> 00:31:46,906
Jednu moju cigaru?

331
00:31:47,698 --> 00:31:50,034
eljela sam tvoj okus u
mojim ustima.

332
00:31:53,912 --> 00:31:55,914
Nemaš nikavog srama.

333
00:31:57,040 --> 00:31:59,334
Nema ništa sramno ako
se volimo.

334
00:32:00,085 --> 00:32:02,086
Voliš li me? Julia?

335
00:32:02,754 --> 00:32:04,422
Voliš li me?

336
00:32:05,339 --> 00:32:07,550
Ili nisi tip koji voli?

337
00:32:47,628 --> 00:32:49,463
Zaboravio sam ti reci.

338
00:32:51,298 --> 00:32:53,800
Dolazi nam gost u nedjelju.

339
00:32:55,093 --> 00:32:56,469
Da?

340
00:32:57,512 --> 00:32:58,763
Da...

341
00:32:58,930 --> 00:33:01,057
...pravi privatni istraitelj...

342
00:33:02,683 --> 00:33:04,852
...cak iz Delawarea.

343
00:33:06,436 --> 00:33:08,772
Emily ga je poslala.

344
00:33:09,064 --> 00:33:11,816
Da. Detektiv Downs.

345
00:33:12,108 --> 00:33:14,277
Rekao si Detektiv Downs?

346
00:33:14,402 --> 00:33:17,196
Ne brini, samo eli
vidjeti da si dobro...

347
00:33:17,905 --> 00:33:20,574
...i sretna i stvarno moja supruga.

348
00:33:21,659 --> 00:33:25,996
- I onda je ova glupost gotova.
- Kad ce ta ptica prestati kreštati?

349
00:33:28,123 --> 00:33:29,291
Julia.

350
00:33:35,379 --> 00:33:38,048
Pazi, stie.

351
00:33:52,353 --> 00:33:54,021
O, ne.

352
00:33:58,734 --> 00:34:01,778
Don Luis, pogledajte. Mrtav je.

353
00:34:03,155 --> 00:34:04,614
Samo je pjevao.

354
00:34:04,739 --> 00:34:07,075
Sad ne pjeva, zar ne?

355
00:34:08,326 --> 00:34:11,120
Izgleda kao da mu je slomljen
njegov mali vrat.

356
00:34:12,163 --> 00:34:15,958
Odnesite ga.
Ne elim da ga Julija vidi.

357
00:35:08,881 --> 00:35:11,300
Kako je osoba umrla na
ovom instrumentu?

358
00:35:13,885 --> 00:35:15,679
Mislim da...

359
00:35:17,472 --> 00:35:20,350
...mu je okretanje tocka
slomilo vrat.

360
00:35:21,517 --> 00:35:23,185
A ako nije?

361
00:35:24,228 --> 00:35:26,063
Da li se onda udavi?

362
00:35:28,107 --> 00:35:29,358
Da li se bojiš?

363
00:35:32,861 --> 00:35:33,820
Ne.

364
00:35:34,571 --> 00:35:36,573
Julia se ne boji.

365
00:35:38,574 --> 00:35:40,034
Ali Bonny da.

366
00:35:41,744 --> 00:35:45,706
Ne razumijem. Tko je Bonny?

367
00:35:50,710 --> 00:35:52,170
Tko je Bonny?

368
00:35:54,547 --> 00:35:56,215
Traim Mr. Vargasa.

369
00:35:56,341 --> 00:35:58,634
To je pitanje koje
ce Luis uskoro pitati.

370
00:36:04,640 --> 00:36:05,974
Mr. Vargas?

371
00:36:06,933 --> 00:36:08,226
Moje ime je Russell.

372
00:36:09,102 --> 00:36:10,520
Emily Russell.

373
00:36:10,812 --> 00:36:12,647
Ja sam Julijina sestra.

374
00:36:14,107 --> 00:36:19,069
Pa razumijete kako sam se
uznemirila primajuci ovo pismo.

375
00:36:19,528 --> 00:36:20,696
Uznemirila?

376
00:36:20,988 --> 00:36:25,158
Ali... mislio sam da ce
vam biti drago kad ga primite.

377
00:36:26,660 --> 00:36:28,495
Ovo pismo, gospodine...

378
00:36:29,162 --> 00:36:32,331
...pisano da odgovori na
ono koje sam ja poslala...

379
00:36:32,665 --> 00:36:35,001
...i potpisano njezinim
imenom...

380
00:36:35,501 --> 00:36:37,503
...nije od Julie.

381
00:36:39,630 --> 00:36:41,715
Naravno da je.

382
00:36:42,341 --> 00:36:43,550
Ja sam ga poslao.

383
00:36:43,675 --> 00:36:45,719
Nije pisano od moje sestre.

384
00:36:45,802 --> 00:36:47,220
Miss Russell.

385
00:36:52,516 --> 00:36:55,019
ao mi je.

386
00:36:55,186 --> 00:36:58,063
Nemojte biti uznemireni.
Kunem vam se-

387
00:36:58,147 --> 00:37:00,273
Kunite se koliko elite.

388
00:37:03,985 --> 00:37:07,447
To nije Julijin rukopis.

389
00:37:07,989 --> 00:37:10,366
To je rukopis stranca.

390
00:37:10,992 --> 00:37:12,785
Nepoznate osobe.

391
00:37:13,827 --> 00:37:15,287
Meni nepoznate.

392
00:37:44,397 --> 00:37:47,233
- Gdje je ona?
- Mislio sam poslati po vas.

393
00:37:47,316 --> 00:37:48,651
Gdje je ona?

394
00:37:49,693 --> 00:37:51,487
Odlazi. Izlazi!

395
00:38:02,580 --> 00:38:03,748
Gdje je otišla?

396
00:38:03,831 --> 00:38:07,793
Ne znam. Poslala me je
u poštu. Kad sam se vratio-

397
00:38:47,913 --> 00:38:51,041
Nece se vratiti, zar ne, Sara?

398
00:38:51,291 --> 00:38:52,750
Nikad ni nije bila ovdje.

399
00:38:54,877 --> 00:38:56,837
Bili ste oenjeni za san.

400
00:38:57,838 --> 00:39:00,090
San koji vam je ukrao dušu.

401
00:39:25,822 --> 00:39:28,158
Luis! Što je?

402
00:39:33,412 --> 00:39:38,167
Vaša ena se pojavila pet
minuta prije zatvaranja.

403
00:39:38,500 --> 00:39:42,837
Kako ste eljeli, dao sam joj
pun pristup na vaše racune.

404
00:39:43,922 --> 00:39:45,965
Vaše stanje na zatvaranju bilo je...

405
00:39:46,466 --> 00:39:49,594
...51 dolar i 40 centa
na jednom racunu...

406
00:39:49,802 --> 00:39:51,595
...10 dolara na drugom.

407
00:39:57,142 --> 00:40:00,437
Kako sam objasnio vašoj eni,
zatvoriti oba racuna totalno...

408
00:40:00,478 --> 00:40:03,148
...trebao bi vaš potpis.

409
00:40:08,819 --> 00:40:10,154
ao mi je.

410
00:40:39,514 --> 00:40:40,807
Don Luis?

411
00:41:12,836 --> 00:41:15,171
Mora da je bog bio
Ijut na tebe taj dan...

412
00:41:15,672 --> 00:41:18,633
...kad ti je dopustio da pogledaš
lice te ene.

413
00:41:32,103 --> 00:41:34,772
elim je nazad. Sara...

414
00:41:37,358 --> 00:41:39,026
...elim je nazad.

415
00:41:41,945 --> 00:41:45,490
Ne, carino. Zašto?

416
00:41:47,075 --> 00:41:49,577
Zašto ju ponovno eliš nazad?

417
00:42:25,443 --> 00:42:27,570
Ne, ovo nije Ijubavna prica.

418
00:42:29,447 --> 00:42:31,574
Ovo je prica o Ijubavi.

419
00:42:34,118 --> 00:42:37,829
O onima koji su joj se prepustili,
i cijeni koju su platili.

420
00:42:41,374 --> 00:42:44,586
i o onima koji su pobjegli od
nje zato jer su se preplašili...

421
00:42:46,170 --> 00:42:49,507
...ili zato što nisu vjerovali.
da se ona isplati

422
00:42:52,217 --> 00:42:53,886
Ona je pobjegla.

423
00:42:54,887 --> 00:42:56,221
On je odustao.

424
00:42:56,638 --> 00:42:57,931
Mr. Vargas?

425
00:42:59,933 --> 00:43:01,601
Walter Downs.

426
00:43:04,854 --> 00:43:06,939
Koja sretna slucajnost.

427
00:43:08,065 --> 00:43:09,400
O, da.

428
00:43:10,943 --> 00:43:12,611
Sjecam vas se.

429
00:43:18,491 --> 00:43:22,161
I vlasti ovdje nisu mogle
ništa napraviti?

430
00:43:25,331 --> 00:43:26,999
Nakon svega...

431
00:43:28,834 --> 00:43:30,502
...nije bilo zlocina.

432
00:43:31,878 --> 00:43:36,716
Bila je moja ena. Samo je uzela
ono što sam joj dao

433
00:43:39,469 --> 00:43:40,803
Vaš novac.

434
00:43:42,847 --> 00:43:44,306
I vašu Ijubav.

435
00:43:47,101 --> 00:43:48,810
I niste ništa posumnjali?

436
00:43:53,982 --> 00:43:58,820
Cini mi se da znam puno manje
o enama nego što sam mislio.

437
00:43:59,820 --> 00:44:01,072
A ja znam previše.

438
00:44:01,489 --> 00:44:03,949
Nemam baš neke koristi od njih...

439
00:44:04,325 --> 00:44:06,285
...osim onog najpotrebnijeg.

440
00:44:06,743 --> 00:44:09,913
Za pravo druenje,
preferiram muško društvo.

441
00:44:11,289 --> 00:44:12,624
Slušajte me.

442
00:44:14,459 --> 00:44:16,127
Moete li je naci?

443
00:44:20,005 --> 00:44:21,340
Moda.

444
00:44:23,175 --> 00:44:26,011
Ali, trenutno sam...

445
00:44:26,094 --> 00:44:30,098
...zauzet u pronalaenju prave
Julije, one koju ste trebali oeniti.

446
00:44:32,684 --> 00:44:34,352
Jeste li ju našli?

447
00:44:35,519 --> 00:44:37,480
Jeste li ju našli?

448
00:44:39,690 --> 00:44:40,983
Još ne.

449
00:44:41,066 --> 00:44:43,235
Ako budete...

450
00:44:43,527 --> 00:44:46,863
...moda vas odvede do Julije
koju sam ja oenio.

451
00:44:48,281 --> 00:44:49,574
Moda.

452
00:44:50,742 --> 00:44:52,034
I obrnuto.

453
00:44:54,912 --> 00:44:59,208
Platit cu vam koliko god treba,
ako ju moete naci za mene.

454
00:44:59,791 --> 00:45:01,626
To je sve što elim.

455
00:45:02,252 --> 00:45:05,213
Onda pretpostavljam da ste
nadoknadili vaše gubitke.

456
00:45:06,256 --> 00:45:09,092
Rekao sam da cu platiti
koliko god elite.

457
00:45:09,467 --> 00:45:10,801
Platit cu.

458
00:45:10,968 --> 00:45:13,304
Da, vjerujem da budete.

459
00:45:14,138 --> 00:45:16,140
A ako nağem vašu Juliju?

460
00:45:16,473 --> 00:45:18,934
Aka vam ju dovedem...

461
00:45:19,768 --> 00:45:21,520
...ili dovedem vas do nje...

462
00:45:22,937 --> 00:45:25,565
...što ce vam to
dobroga donijeti?

463
00:45:26,274 --> 00:45:27,358
Novac je otišao.

464
00:45:29,277 --> 00:45:30,569
Ljubav...

465
00:45:31,362 --> 00:45:32,655
...uništena.

466
00:45:34,073 --> 00:45:36,283
Što bi još mogli
htjeti od nje?

467
00:45:38,410 --> 00:45:40,245
Što bi još mogli eljeti?

468
00:45:46,584 --> 00:45:48,252
elim je ubiti.

469
00:46:09,897 --> 00:46:12,357
Da, sjecam se te dame.

470
00:46:12,816 --> 00:46:15,110
Mršava, tamna i jako...

471
00:46:15,986 --> 00:46:20,156
Sjecam se kad je dolazila niz palubu
i povjetarac joj je uhvatio suknju.

472
00:46:20,615 --> 00:46:22,116
Dolazila je prema meni.

473
00:46:22,325 --> 00:46:26,996
Brzo ju je uhvatila i
onda mi se osmjehnula.

474
00:46:27,913 --> 00:46:31,249
Mislim da je putovala s
grupom Americkih glumaca...

475
00:46:31,333 --> 00:46:32,501
...na turneji po otoku.

476
00:46:32,792 --> 00:46:34,961
O da, sjecam se.

477
00:46:35,336 --> 00:46:38,423
Zamotala je malo salate
u njezinu salvetu.

478
00:46:39,173 --> 00:46:43,219
